comment: Leontocoides section, probably C. popovii or else mixed hybrids including genes from popovii, maracandica, and ledbouriana. Fresh seed which should be sown as quickly as possible
(OP), goes very deep and will grow on acid sand
(C. oliganthum x C. procerum)? 2', red leaves, pink flowers, Z 8b. "I grow it in full sun with average water. A very nice plant that can be grown in bog conditions" FEW
